data.description: Looking for a fantastic, move-in ready townhome where comfort meets contemporary living, providing ample space for both relaxation and functionality?  Step inside the 1,661 square feet of well-designed living space, where a thoughtful layout enhances the flow of daily life. The main floor features an open-concept living area, seamlessly connecting the living room, dining space, and a modern kitchen. There's a combination of tile in the entry way and new LVP flooring throughout most of the first floor living areas, no carpet here! The kitchen is stylish with plenty of room to spread out and a pantry, making meal preparation a joy. Upstairs you'll discover the three comfortably sized bedrooms, each offering a retreat for rest and privacy. The primary bath has dual vanities, designed with both aesthetics and practicality in mind. The laundry closet is also located upstairs for convenience. This two-story townhome includes a coveted one-car garage, ensuring both parking ease and additional storage space, and two assigned parking spaces in front. Imagine the ease of unloading groceries or stepping directly into your home during inclement weather. One of the highlights of this property is the screened porch, offering a perfect spot to enjoy the outdoors without the intrusion of insects. Whether sipping your morning coffee or unwinding in the evening, this space becomes a tranquil extension of your home. And the private yard is enclosed with a white vinyl fence for easy maintenance. Located in a desirable location, this townhome provides not only a comfortable living space but also easy access to local amenities, schools, and entertainment options. Don't miss the opportunity to this your new home for the Holidays!
